citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:15pm on
24-Feb-20.
Inspector arrived at the facility and contact was made with the licensee by phone. No responsible adult was
available to conduct the inspection that day.
